{
    "title": "句末分号",
    "type": "topic",
    "order": 0,
    "desc": [
        "';'分号在js代码中不是必需的,例如:",
        "\n\r\t\tvar name = 'Hulu';\n\t\tvar age = 16;",
        "等价于:",
        "\n\r\t\tvar name = 'Hulu'",
        "\t\tvar age = 16",
        "但当多条语句写于一行时,必须加分号",
        "\n\r\t\tvar name = 'Hulu'; var age = 16",
        "语句之间必须以分号间隔"
    ],
    "code": "请回答:",
    "question": {
        "content": "下列哪种书写形式是没错误的?",
        "options": ["var name = 'Hulu'  var age = 16","var name = 'Hulu'; var age = 16", "var name = 'Hulu'  var age = 16;"]
    },
    "answer": {
        "value": "var name = 'Hulu'; var age = 16",
        "explains": [
            "<p>JS中分号的存在是为了在一行中<strong>分割多条语句</strong>.</p>"
        ]
    }
}
